content.text: Good, the schema has the relevant columns. Now let me query for the claim.

input.command:
sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "
SELECT MAX(f.[Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)] / f.[Enrollment (Ages 5-17)]) as max_free_rate
FROM satscores s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cds = f.CDSCode
WHERE CAST(s.NumGE1500 AS REAL) / s.NumTstTakr > 0.3
  AND s.NumTstTakr > 0
  AND f.[Enrollment (Ages 5-17)] > 0;
"
